c: 10
v: 90
t: "Uye takava tinoita vana veIzrairi kuti vave vanodarika gungwa, uye Farawo nehondo yake akatevera ane kudzvinyirira neruvengo, kusvika apo paainyudzwa, akati: “Ndinotenda kuti hakuna umwe mwari kunze kweuyo anotendwa nevana veIzrairi, uye ndiri umwe wemaMuslim (avo vanozvipira kuna Allah).”"